Badmorda, that argument goes down a two way street. If you only want to raid because you get gear then why in the world does raiding exist at all? You are making it plainly and blatantly obvious that you would not want to do it if there were alternatives to other items/gear/etc....  In fact the very quote I just used from you admits that you would not want to raid if there were other paths to follow in the game for similar rewards. 
