I answered this in my response to your 4 questions. And also I will point out again that I dont necessarily think ALL of the alternative paths or progression, acquistition, etc... should just be 6 people. Some maybe, yes. Some not. I will reiterate that I simply think raiding of sizes that exist today is a burden that many people who would like to enjoy the higher end zones and gear cannot or do not want to put up with. If you enjoy it then great. Continuing doing so, there is nothing wrong with that. Its a BIG virtual world. Much like real life. Real life has many paths and avenues to achieve goals. Why can a virtual fantasy game not offer this? I touched on this earlier in my reply and you can refer to that.
